Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:59.22,IN2,,0,0,0,,拯救了像我這般無助的人\N{\fs57}That sav'd a wretch like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:12.14,IN2,,0,0,0,,我曾迷失，如今已被找回\N{\fs57}I once was lost, but now I am found,
